{"tid":965393,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"葉劉遊荷蘭遭電單車黨劫財","createTime":"2019-01-02T04:20:39.000Z","updateTime":"2019-01-02T04:36:25.000Z","uid":144039,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"b00932b10270b9bc0a2d88033132d0ae895fa52d","tid":965393,"uid":144039,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-02T04:20:39.000Z","msg":"好彩唔係劫色<img src=\"/assets/faces/dogxm/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dogxm/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n不少立法會議員都會趁著聖誕跨年假期，出外旅遊散心，其中新民黨主席葉劉淑儀就偕女兒歐遊，近日就發生驚險事。葉劉今日（1日）在Facebook發文透露，自己現身在荷蘭阿姆斯特丹，遇到「電單車黨」，險些被搶劫，幸最終力保不失，只受了點輕傷，現時已準備回港，看來保安局前局長亦不能幸免，險遭逢橫禍。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.hk01.com/%E6%94%BF%E6%83%85/277587/%E6%94%BF%E5%A3%87%E8%AB%B8%E4%BA%8B%E7%94%BA-%E8%91%89%E5%8A%89%E9%81%8A%E8%8D%B7%E8%98%AD%E9%81%87-%E9%9B%BB%E5%96%AE%E8%BB%8A%E9%BB%A8-%E9%9A%AA%E8%A2%AB%E5%8A%AB%E8%B2%A1%E5%8F%97%E8%BC%95%E5%82%B7?utm_medium=Social&amp;utm_source=fbpost_link&amp;utm_campaign=news\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hk01.com%2F%25E6%2594%25BF%25E6%2583%2585%2F277587%2F%25E6%2594%25BF%25E5%25A3%2587%25E8%25AB%25B8%25E4%25BA%258B%25E7%2594%25BA-%25E8%2591%2589%25E5%258A%2589%25E9%2581%258A%25E8%258D%25B7%25E8%2598%25AD%25E9%2581%2587-%25E9%259B%25BB%25E5%2596%25AE%25E8%25BB%258A%25E9%25BB%25A8-%25E9%259A%25AA%25E8%25A2%25AB%25E5%258A%25AB%25E8%25B2%25A1%25E5%258F%2597%25E8%25BC%2595%25E5%2582%25B7%3Futm_medium%3DSocial%26utm_source%3Dfbpost_link%26utm_campaign%3Dnews&d=MXhVha7Nm3DnEh1U5ZIZVmi1w7%2FDyS2Kz%2BsYtkalU0Y%3D&h=a6185543\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.hk01.com/%E6%94%BF%E6%83%85/277587/%E6%94%BF%E5%A3%87%E8%AB%B8%E4%BA%8B%E7%94%BA-%E8%91%89%E5%8A%89%E9%81%8A%E8%8D%B7%E8%98%AD%E9%81%87-%E9%9B%BB%E5%96%AE%E8%BB%8A%E9%BB%A8-%E9%9A%AA%E8%A2%AB%E5%8A%AB%E8%B2%A1%E5%8F%97%E8%BC%95%E5%82%B7?utm_medium=Social&amp;utm_source=fbpost_link&amp;utm_campaign=news</a>"},{"pid":"39ad3db2106d353c385e2705a84b63dddd385aa5","tid":965393,"uid"